# office_map.pgm
# Portable GreyMap (binary) — 2-D occupancy grid of the office environment.
# Resolution: 0.05 m/pixel   Size: 400 x 320 pixels  (~20 m x 16 m)
# White (255) = free space, Black (0) = obstacle, Grey (205) = unknown.
#
# This is a placeholder text stub.  In a real deployment this file would be a
# binary PGM produced by ros2 run nav2_map_server map_saver_cli or by the
# occupancy_grid_mapper when save_map() is called.
#
# To regenerate from a bag file:
#   ros2 run nav2_map_server map_saver_cli -f data/maps/office_map \
#       --ros-args -p use_sim_time:=false
400 320
255
